Interface ConceptCreationViewI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IsaacViewI, PopupViewI
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConceptCreationWizard

    @Contract
public interface ConceptCreationViewI
extends PopupViewI
    ConceptCreationViewI An interface that allows the creation of a ConceptCreationView implementation, which will be a JavaFX component that extends PopupViewI. The popup is intended to be a wizard style window that will guide the user through the creation of a new concept.
